      "source": "He made his Serie A debut on 17 June 2001 against <59>Juventus FC</59> He played a few more Serie A games for Atalanta in October 2003, after he was returned from loan to <66>Lumezzane</66> of the third division in <73>2002–03 Serie C1</73>.",
